  "text": "In the reference [CITATION_1] , the authors show a case study to convert automatically business processes written in BPEL-WSCDL to timed automata and to verify subsequently them by the UPPAAL model checker [49] . The authors are currently implementing a tool for the automatic translation that utilizes UPPAAL.",
